OL,3,CHow are South Asian communities
OL,4,Ccelebrating their heritage in Wales?
OL,6,FSouth Asian Heritage Month is back for
OL,7,Fits fifth year, and people have come
OL,8,Ftogether at the Morganstown Village
OL,9,FHall to mark the occasion.
OL,11,FSujatha Thaladi, organiser and founder
OL,12,Fof Mentor Ring, says the event is
OL,13,Fabout celebrating the culture.
OL,15,FShe said: "We tried to bring in as
OL,16,Fmany people from different countries.
OL,17,FThey are going to perform, dance and
OL,18,Fshowcase their culture and talk about
OL,19,Ftheir heritage.
