OL,3,CHow are South Asian communities
OL,4,Ccelebrating their heritage in Wales?
OL,6,F"South Asian communities have
OL,7,Fcontributed not only to the UK but
OL,8,Fthroughout the globe."
OL,10,FWhat is South Asian Heritage month?
OL,12,FIt was set up in 2019 to celebrate and
OL,13,Fhonour the contributions of South
OL,14,FAsian communities to the UK.
OL,16,FIt is celebrated from 18 July until 17
OL,17,FAugust.
