OL,3,CHow are South Asian communities
OL,4,Ccelebrating their heritage in Wales?
OL,6,FThis year's theme is 'Free To Be Me'
OL,7,Fwhich encourages people to share the
OL,8,Funique experiences that have made them
OL,9,Fwho they are today and celebrate being
OL,10,Fthemselves as well as honouring their
OL,11,Froots.
OL,13,FOne person attending the event said:
OL,14,F"We are free to be here, to be doing
OL,15,Fwhat we like, that's what it means for
OL,16,Fus."
OL,18,FAnother performer added: "I like my
OL,19,Fcommunity, the history, the culture
OL,20,Fwe've been through. So, it's important
OL,21,Ffor me to be sharing that."
