OL,3,CHow are South Asian communities
OL,4,Ccelebrating their heritage in Wales?
OL,6,FWhy do we celebrate South Asian
OL,7,FHeritage Month?
OL,9,FIt is celebrated to embrace members of
OL,10,FSouth Asian communities who have lived
OL,11,Fhere in the UK since World War 2 and
OL,12,Fmore so after the Indian Independence
OL,13,Fand Partition in 1947.
OL,15,FIn Morganstown, they celebrated the
OL,16,Fmonth by showcasing different dance
OL,17,Fforms, including Traditional Tamil
OL,18,FTribal dance and a fusion dance from
OL,19,FSri Lanka.
