OL,3,CHow are South Asian communities
OL,4,Ccelebrating their heritage in Wales?
OL,6,FOne of the oldest classical dance
OL,7,Fforms that originated from the temples
OL,8,Fof south India is Bharatanatyam.
OL,10,FMegan Lloyd from India Dance Wales
OL,11,Fpursued this traditional dance herself
OL,12,Fand has now combined it with Welsh
OL,13,Ffolk tunes.
OL,15,FShe said : "I think it's a beautiful
OL,16,Fdance form that everyone can enjoy.
OL,17,FYou can enjoy it for the spectacle of
OL,18,Fit, just for the bright colours. You
OL,19,Fcan enjoy it for the music or the
OL,20,Frhythmic patterns and it tells stories
OL,21,Fwith the hands."
