OL,3,CHow are South Asian communities
OL,4,Ccelebrating their heritage in Wales?
OL,6,FThere are eight countries that make up
OL,7,FSouth Asia: Afghanistan, Bangladesh,
OL,8,FBhutan, India, The Maldives, Nepal,
OL,9,FPakistan and Sri Lanka.
OL,11,FBut they all share a deep
OL,12,Funderstanding of each other's values
OL,13,Fand embrace their differences.
